---
import MarketingLayout from "../../layouts/MarketingLayout.astro";
const lastUpdated = "May 11, 2026";
---

<MarketingLayout title="Privacy Policy — Madar AI" description="How Madar AI collects, uses, and protects your data.">
  <section class="pt-32 pb-24 px-6 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <div class="mb-12">
      <div class="text-[10px] font-mono uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-[#F97316] mb-3">Legal</div>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-semibold tracking-tight mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-[11px] font-mono text-white/40">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
    </div>

    <div class="prose-madar space-y-8">
      <section>
        <h2>1. Who We Are</h2>
        <p>
          Madar AI is a product of Zyrix Global Technologies, a company headquartered in Istanbul, Türkiye. In this policy, "Madar," "we," "us," and "our" refer to Zyrix Global Technologies operating under the Madar AI brand. "You" refers to the individual or organization using our services.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>2. What We Collect</h2>
        <p>We collect the following categories of information:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Account data:</strong> name, email address, password (hashed), company, and role.</li>
          <li><strong>Connected app data:</strong> when you connect platforms like App Store Connect, Google Play, RevenueCat, or AppsFlyer, we ingest the metrics and events these platforms make available via their APIs.</li>
          <li><strong>Usage data:</strong> pages visited, features used, and actions taken within the Madar dashboard.</li>
          <li><strong>Communications:</strong> messages you send us through contact forms, email, or support channels.</li>
          <li><strong>Technical data:</strong> IP address, browser type, device type, and timestamps.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>3. How We Use Your Data</h2>
        <p>We use your data only to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Operate and improve the Madar product</li>
          <li>Generate the AI insights, forecasts, and benchmarks you came to us for</li>
          <li>Send you account, security, and product update notifications</li>
          <li>Respond to your support requests</li>
          <li>Comply with our legal obligations</li>
        </ul>
        <p>We do not sell your data. We do not use your data to train third-party AI models.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>4. Benchmark Aggregation</h2>
        <p>
          When we publish industry benchmarks, the data is fully anonymized and aggregated across many apps. Your individual app's metrics are never identifiable in any benchmark report. You can opt out of benchmark aggregation at any time from your account settings.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>5. Data Storage and Security</h2>
        <p>
          Your data is stored on Supabase infrastructure in the Mumbai (ap-south-1) region. All data is encrypted in transit (TLS 1.3) and at rest (AES-256). Access to production systems is restricted to a small number of authorized engineers under audit.
        </p>
        <p>
          We retain your data for as long as your account is active. If you delete your account, we delete your personal data within 30 days, except where retention is required by law.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>6. Your Rights</h2>
        <p>Depending on your jurisdiction, you may have the right to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Access the personal data we hold about you</li>
          <li>Correct inaccurate data</li>
          <li>Delete your data ("right to be forgotten")</li>
          <li>Export your data in a portable format</li>
          <li>Object to or restrict certain processing</li>
          <li>Withdraw consent at any time</li>
        </ul>
        <p>To exercise any of these rights, email <a href="mailto:privacy@madarai.co">privacy@madarai.co</a>.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>7. Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>We use the following third-party services to operate Madar:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Supabase</strong> — database and authentication</li>
          <li><strong>Cloudflare</strong> — hosting, CDN, and security</li>
          <li><strong>Resend</strong> — transactional email</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Each of these providers has their own privacy policy, which governs how they handle data we send them.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>8. Cookies</h2>
        <p>
          We use essential cookies for authentication and session management. We do not use third-party advertising or tracking cookies on our marketing site. If we ever add analytics cookies, we will request your consent first.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>9. International Transfers</h2>
        <p>
          Madar operates globally. Your data may be transferred to and processed in countries other than your own. Where required, we rely on Standard Contractual Clauses and similar safeguards to protect international data transfers.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>10. Children</h2>
        <p>
          Madar is not directed at children under 16. We do not knowingly collect personal data from children. If you believe a child has provided us with personal data, contact us and we will delete it.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>11. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>
          We may update this policy from time to time. When we do, we will revise the "Last updated" date at the top. For material changes, we will notify you by email or in-product notice before the changes take effect.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>12. Contact</h2>
        <p>
          Questions about this policy? Email <a href="mailto:privacy@madarai.co">privacy@madarai.co</a>.
        </p>
        <p class="text-[11px] font-mono text-white/40 mt-6">
          Zyrix Global Technologies<br/>
          Istanbul, Türkiye
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </section>

  <style is:global>
    .prose-madar h2 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      color: white;
    }
    .prose-madar p {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75);
      line-height: 1.75;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      font-size: 1rem;
    }
    .prose-madar ul, .prose-madar ol {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75);
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      padding-left: 1.5rem;
    }
    .prose-madar ul li { list-style: disc; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; line-height: 1.7; }
    .prose-madar ol li { list-style: decimal; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; line-height: 1.7; }
    .prose-madar strong { color: white; font-weight: 600; }
    .prose-madar a { color: #F97316; text-decoration: underline; text-underline-offset: 3px; }
    .prose-madar a:hover { color: #FB923C; }
  </style>
</MarketingLayout>